sentences.english: Pathorphological observation of naturally occurring and experimental pullorum disease of chicks was conducted.
sentences.chinese: 对自发性和实验性雏鸡白痢病进行了病理形态学观察。

sentences.english: These chicks are at great risk from horizontal infection from hatching onwards.
sentences.chinese: 这样的雏鸡自出雏之日起，就受到被水平感染的威胁。

sentences.english: What Happens when Chicks Get Cold?
sentences.chinese: 当雏鸡受凉时会发生什么？

sentences.english: The effect of Chinese herbal medicine mixture on the immune function and interferon production of the chickens were studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了中药合剂对雏鸡免疫功能及干扰素产生的影响。

sentences.english: The girl is a spring chicken compared to her 60 year-old boyfriend.
sentences.chinese: 和她60岁的男朋友相比，这个姑娘就是一只雏鸡。

sentences.english: The paper covers one case of symptom and pathology-dissection of the Rose chicken.
sentences.chinese: 本文报道了一例罗斯雏鸡的患病症状与病理解剖情况。

sentences.english: Includes complete instructions for creating the Black Pullet .
sentences.chinese: 为打造完整指令包括黑色雏鸡。

sentences.english: Many factors may affect the hatchability and subsequent quality of the day old chicks.
sentences.chinese: 很多因素影响种鸡孵化率及出生雏鸡质量。

sentences.english: As a result fewer females breed and fewer chicks are produced.
sentences.chinese: 结果，现在雌雄物种越来越少，生产的雏鸡也在变少。

sentences.english: In particular, a small smoked chicken, delicious meat, crisp flesh and blood are very first chew.
sentences.chinese: 尤其熏出的小雏鸡，肉味鲜美，骨肉俱酥，很有嚼头。
